arguments.response_text: Hi! I moved to Chicago about 10 years ago for school at DePaul University and it was a little scary at first because I didn't know anybody but I'm so glad I moved and I've been here for a long time and it's been one of the best decisions of my life.
arguments.response_summary: The responder shares their experience of moving to Chicago for school and how it has been a positive experience over time.
arguments.matched_prompt: How did you and your family build a life in Chicago?
